metadata.Plot: Philippe is married man with an appetite for women. When the affair is discovered, a vengeful spouse hijacks their date and holds Philippe hostage, ready to extract a cruel, psychological revenge. Now faced with losing everything, Philippe is forced to confront the true nature of love and hate and just how far one person will go to save a marriage. And then, something unexpected happens, plunging Philippe and his mistress into an even greater nightmare.
